headline: Principal Financial Group (PFG) Returns to Profitability, Challenging Persistent Bearish Narratives on Earnings Quality
summary: Principal Financial Group (PFG) has reversed a five-year trend of declining earnings, becoming profitable in the most recent year with high quality earnings now in focus. Shares trade at $82.20, which stands well below the estimated fair value of $203.24. PFG’s price-to-earnings ratio of 11.6x is also lower than key industry benchmarks.
